# portfolio_2026 — AI context

Before editing: read `docs/cursor-workflow.md`, then the relevant doc from `docs/` (design-system, content-structure, architecture, project-overview).

Human-oriented Cursor tips: `docs/cursor-best-practices.md`.

While editing this repo:

- Prefer CSS variables from `src/styles/base.css`; no `overflow-x: hidden` on `body`.
- After substantive changes: run `npm run build`; append one line to Recent Changes in `cursor-workflow.md`.
- No em dashes in user-facing copy; keep tone direct, not “AI brochure” tone.

Keep rules in `.cursor/rules/` short; put detail in `docs/`.
